{"tid":1546013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拯救南亞手足！南亞手足一齊圍狗屋！","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T23:03:19.000Z","uid":318932,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa577d62d8dbe80ad2ccaeb188354a346233893d","tid":1546013,"uid":318932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】旺角警署外再有示威者聚集，有人分別燒著雜物及投擲硬物入警署，警方一度出示橙旗警告後凌晨出動驅散，事後拘捕一名16歲非華裔少年。<br />\n<br />\n數十名示威者晚上再在警署外聚集，對面的一段太子道西站滿人，其間有人打開傘陣，懷疑把雜物點火，並把燃燒中的物品放入警署外的水馬上，地下亦有其他燃燒中的雜物。<br />\n<br />\n警署內有多名防暴警員持槍戒備，有示威者向警員照射雷射光，警方舉橙旗警告要求示威者立即離開，否則會發射橡膠子彈或布袋彈。<br />\n<br />\n至凌晨十二時許，有兩名示威者持硬物擲向警署，有玻璃碎散落地上，警方再次舉旗警告，大批防暴警員出動，分別向西洋菜南街及彌敦道推進。示威者四散逃去後，警方返回警署。<br />\n<br />\n事後警方在旺角區拘捕一名16歲非華裔少年，他涉嫌縱火及刑事毀壞被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361817&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c0d41b8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361817&h=c4931322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361817</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人知道佢而家比啲狗帶咗去邊度？！</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫晒所有南亞手足，一齊去圍狗屋！</span></span>"},{"pid":"79b1e81c85e9e68ae5ba60ca5f48dc44d7e957fc","tid":1546013,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />